# mods-enabled/auth_modules
#
# pap, chap, mschap, preprocess, attr_filter, and detail are already
# enabled by the image's default mods-enabled/ symlinks pointing to
# mods-available/. Redefining them here causes startup errors because
# our simplified versions lack internal variable references.
#
# This file is intentionally minimal. The image defaults handle all
# standard auth modules. Add overrides here only if you need to change
# a specific module's settings, and copy the full definition from
# /etc/raddb/mods-available/ inside the container as your starting point.
